{"id":582677,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/【麻辣总局】因成功预测口误-微博网友遭封号/","date":"2018-04-12T07:59:08Z","modified":"2018-04-12T10:15:29Z","title":"【麻辣总局】因成功“预测口误” 微博网友遭封号","content":"<p>4月12日，有微博网友吐槽称，自己曾在4月3日发布了一条“这次习近平会在博鳌亚洲论坛读错什么字呢？”结果在4月10日习近平再度读稿口误后，自己因为此条消息遭遇封号。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUJUSXUAEF9tq.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-582691\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUJUSXUAEF9tq.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUJUSXUAEF9tq.jpg 1013w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUJUSXUAEF9tq-253x300.jpg 253w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUJUSXUAEF9tq-768x910.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUJUSXUAEF9tq-864x1024.jpg 864w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUKPpWAAAKn4H.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-582692\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUKPpWAAAKn4H.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"395\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUKPpWAAAKn4H.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUKPpWAAAKn4H-300x264.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUKPpWAAAKn4H-768x675.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DafUKPpWAAAKn4H-1024x900.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>背景新闻：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>【明报专讯】国家主席习近平4月10日于博鳌开幕典礼上，公布中国未来4项扩大开放政策，其中在「主动扩大进口」部分出现口误，将「中国不以追求贸易顺差为目标」，说成「中国不以追求贸易逆差为目标」。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a title=\"明报 | 习近平博鳌开幕典礼口误 顺差读作「逆差」\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/%e6%98%8e%e6%8a%a5-%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e5%8d%9a%e9%b3%8c%e5%bc%80%e5%b9%95%e5%85%b8%e7%a4%bc%e5%8f%a3%e8%af%af-%e9%a1%ba%e5%b7%ae%e8%af%bb%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8c%e9%80%86%e5%b7%ae%e3%80%8d/\">明报 | 习近平博鳌开幕典礼口误 顺差读作「逆差」</a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13789],"tags":[27046,30129,34009,34329,34328,11064,25917,8620,20644,29005,31200,34316,31685]}